{"lastModified":1776406501554,"uri":"c::9511821703::vessel::d17fd160-0c70-11ef-a4f2-cd61f4d4d7df","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sydney, Pittwater, Whitsunday Islands\n\nLuxury superyacht Sirenuse entered the market in 2022 and is available for charter in two of Australia’s most sought-after destinations: the magnificent Whitsundays and the glistening coastline of Sydney.\n\nThis iconic, timeless Monte Carlo build is the largest to date in the MCY collection and described as ‘the most tangible exemplification of the company’s vision’. With incredibly expansive interior spaces, a large Portuguese deck at the bow and a master cabin the entire breadth of the vessel, this yacht is unmatched in its class and comfort.\n\n8 guests will sleep in four elegant cabins with two different configurations to choose from.\n\nThe 70 square metre flybridge consists of two lounges, a dining area and deck chairs. The foredeck is dedicated to ultimate relaxation with a spacious sofa and two large sunpads complete with unobstructed ocean views. Perfect for private entertaining.\n\nA bar welcomes you into the main salon, with a layout featuring two sofas and a dining room with windows that slide open to the sea for al fresco style seating.\n\nWhether you choose to set sail amongst the spectacular islands of the Whitsundays, or cruise through the scenic waterways of Pittwater, you will find yourself in complete solace on board Sirenuse.\n\nFor those looking for a Whitsundays or Sydney superyacht charter, Sirenuse will treat you to an experience second to none.","blueprint":{"name":"SIRENUSE","images":["/media/media::image::c::9511821703::vessel::d17fd160-0c70-11ef-a4f2-cd61f4d4d7df::assets::a1090fc0-0c74-11ef-a4f2-cd61f4d4d7df.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9511821703::vessel::d17fd160-0c70-11ef-a4f2-cd61f4d4d7df::assets::77e264c0-0c74-11ef-a4f2-cd61f4d4d7df.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9511821703::vessel::d17fd160-0c70-11ef-a4f2-cd61f4